<plot>Tobias has guarded the secret of stopping time for years to protect others from its tragic consequences. But now his distant grandson, Toby, determined to live forever, is on the verge of uncovering it. And although he won't listen to the old man's warnings, when he meets his attractive new neighbor Carrie, Tobias hopes for a new chance to stop him before it's too late. It isn't long before Toby finds himself being forced to choose between love and immortality.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?188307</url></doc>
